% Print the numbers for a score reel

% A procedure to convert from mm to points
% stack: n  ->  n
/in { 72 mul } def

% A procedure to convert from mm to points
% stack: n  ->  n
/mm { 2.83465 mul } def

/NewCenturySchlbk-Bold findfont 75 mm scalefont setfont

newpath
1 in 1 in moveto

12					% i				place some integer value on the stack
%2 string			% i (\000)		push a string with one null character in it
(99999999)
cvs					% (i)			format the i value as a printable digit
show				% -				print the string


showpage
